data.description: Location, location! Custom built home convenient to Exits 4 & 1 with NO HOA! Crown molding, beautiful fireplace/mirror in living room, archways throughout, formal dining room currently being used as an office, stainless steel appliances, Primary bedroom with double trey ceiling, jacuzzi tub & shower, walk in closets in every bedroom. Sunroom full of natural light, backyard with privacy fence for pets, greenhouse & storage shed in backyard included. Roof replaced in 2019, Refrigerator 2019, Water Heater 2019, Oven 2022, Dishwasher 2022. Possible assumable mortgage must verify through Navy Fed - owner's current interest rate is 2.5%.
